{"tid":1470034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急】做物資嘅同我入黎","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T04:44:00.000Z","uid":268643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f5560adcf4e74533b4a7331d53c0d996693d01bc","tid":1470034,"uid":268643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:58:07.000Z","msg":"各位發夢夢見自己係做物資嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n自8月5日後<br />\n每次放低物資 整理嘅時候 就會有狗衝出黎捉 <br />\n係長沙灣道 南昌街 冇上電視嘅位置 <br />\n物資手足放低物之後大約十分鐘 <br />\n班豬車就衝到嚟<br />\n速龍就突然從私家車跳車落黎捉<br />\n唯有放棄大量物資<br />\n奪命狂奔<br />\n<br />\n物資手足孭一個小型背囊到達現場<br />\n詢問現場手足有乜嘢缺乏<br />\n再購買比現場手續<br />\n<br />\n咁樣可以保護到一批本身唔係前線身體對抗性冇咁高嘅物資手足 <br />\n<br />\n真係需要逃走 <br />\n真身上所有物資丟棄然之後奪命狂奔<br />\n<br />\n祝物資隊 武運亨昌 <br />\n<br />\n發夢夢見六位物資隊隊員被捉<br />\n心碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今個星期日和理非大遊行大家休息下 去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756fa87d4c0eec1fbb36e538bcf41b25261e76a0","tid":1470034,"uid":11143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:58:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"291e91e006e8681cd0fb9784d9d883bd9d7945fc","tid":1470034,"uid":268643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"756fa87d4c0eec1fbb36e538bcf41b25261e76a0","tid":1470034,"uid":11143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:58:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:00:29.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"029ccda8bb65c785a0e366a28d81057c7c3f8dc7","tid":1470034,"uid":268643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:01:20.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"09c338ed6ec9e89dcf926e4c6c311ff2f1ec6d9a","tid":1470034,"uid":268643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:08:13.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"69564cc87a462b5fb2719d9d067adcbca262ae4d","tid":1470034,"uid":268643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:44:00.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"}]}